1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Written by Nick Ackerman</em></p> <p>Infrastructure and real estate are two areas the world needs to function, at least function with some comfort and efficiency. Cohen Steers Infrastructure Fund (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UTF\" title=\"Cohen&amp;Steers Infrastructure Fund\">UTF</a>) and Cohen &amp; Steers Real Estate Opportunities and Income</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741671-utf-and-rlty-quality-infrastructure-and-real-estate-looking-attractive", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 12:00:00"}, {"id": "4741663", "title": "Old CEO Out, 'New CEO' In - Struggling Intel Is A Bargain Nonetheless", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel Headquarters\" data-id=\"1831946092\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span class=\"highlighted_text\">In my last few articles about Intel Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NEOE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC:CA\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC:CA</a></span>), I was always</span> bullish, and I don\u2019t want to justify myself here in any way. I was clearly wrong about Intel in the last few quarters and obviously too optimistic about Intel</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741663-intel-stock-bargain-despite-ceo-retirement", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 11:47:50"}, {"id": "4741670", "title": "Office CMBS Delinquency Rate Spikes To 10.4%, Just Below Worst Of Financial Crisis Meltdown", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Reverse mortgage application form, financial concept\" data-id=\"1150724195\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Casper1774Studio/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Office-to-residential conversions are growing, but are minuscule because not many towers are suitable for conversion.</em></p> <p>The delinquency rate of office mortgages that have been securitized into commercial mortgage-backed securities (CMBS) spiked by a full percentage point in November</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150724195/image_1150724195.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741670-office-cmbs-delinquency-rate-spikes-to-10-4-percent-just-below-worst-of-financial-crisis-meltdown", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 11:40:00"}, {"id": "4741660", "title": "Semrush: Strong Growth, But Risks Loom Large", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300930633/image_1300930633.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Search Engine Optimization (SEO) Concept On Computer Screen With Two Busines